@startuml sequence_diagram_get_watchlists
title Get Watchlists - Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Application" as APP
database "SQL Database" as DB

User -> APP: GET /api/watchlists

== Authentication & Validation ==
APP -> APP: Validate user authentication and permission

== Fetch User Watchlists ==
APP -> DB: SELECT * FROM watchlist WHERE user_id = :user_id
DB --> APP: watchlists[]
APP --> User: 200 OK { watchlists }
@enduml